e:\n\n``` go\n db.Model(&A{}).AddForeignKey(\"b_id\", \"b(id)\", \"RESTRICT\", \"RESTRICT\")\n```\n\nGenerated Query:\n\n``` sql\n ALTER TABLE \"a\" ADD CONSTRAINT \"a_b_id_foreign\" FOREIGN KEY (\"b_id\") REFERENCES \"b(id)\" ON DELETE RESTRICT ON UPDATE RESTRICT;\n```\n\nExpected query (runs in postgres):\n\n``` sql\nALTER TABLE \"a\" ADD CONSTRAINT \"a_b_id_foreign\" FOREIGN KEY (\"b_id\") REFERENCES b(id) ON DELETE RESTRICT ON UPDATE RESTRICT;\n```\n\nI _think_ the solution is to not QuoteIfPossible on: https://github.com/jinzhu/gorm/blob/0def184b0ca6d0b4d4b772a18b909d35b6cb86a1/scope_private.go#L574 for dest\n\nHope this is helpful for others who use foreign keys :)  I was able to convert all but two of my foreign keys to struct tags (`sql:\"type uuid REFERENCES c(id)\"`), but I encountered this when two tables referred to one another (so I can't change creation ordering, heh)\n","closed_by":{"login":"jinzhu","id":6843,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjY4NDM=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6843?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu","html_url":"https://github.com/jinzhu","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/jinzhu/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/go-gorm/gorm/issues/593/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url